  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to Learn, Hard to Master!</h2> <br>Indigo 7 is a fast-paced multiplayer puzzle game for up to 4 players, with a cool single-player story mode.<br>Wear your swimsuit, dust off your beach tennis rackets, and put batteries in your old radio to enjoy this cool puzzle game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 11 playable characters.<br></li><li> 6 different play modes.<br></li><li> Play alone or with up to 3 friends.<br></li><li> Unlock all the levels, songs, and characters.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adventure Mode</strong></h2>Journey with Nathan and his friends on a musical adventure of love and friendship in 32 episodes, told through a fantastic comic.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle</strong></h2>Fight Your Rivals to See Who Gets the Best Score.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/1b4ebef11f00472f56701ca20693038b.poster.avif?t=1627466718\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/1b4ebef11f00472f56701ca20693038b.webm?t=1627466718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/1b4ebef11f00472f56701ca20693038b.mp4?t=1627466718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Conquest</strong></h2>Conquer all the territory before running out of time and moves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/5f958d40e7fe640a0812d0e820959820.poster.avif?t=1627466718\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/5f958d40e7fe640a0812d0e820959820.webm?t=1627466718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/5f958d40e7fe640a0812d0e820959820.mp4?t=1627466718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Conquest VS</strong></h2>Conquer More territory Than Your Opponents.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/1f8944c6582dede0ff257d84738ef8ea.poster.avif?t=1627466718\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/1f8944c6582dede0ff257d84738ef8ea.webm?t=1627466718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/1f8944c6582dede0ff257d84738ef8ea.mp4?t=1627466718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Party Time</strong></h2>Think quick and act carefully. The fastest-paced mode to keep all your senses on full alert.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/7fc0b5fed90bf5c6c9e71e90cdabe518.poster.avif?t=1627466718\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/7fc0b5fed90bf5c6c9e71e90cdabe518.webm?t=1627466718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/7fc0b5fed90bf5c6c9e71e90cdabe518.mp4?t=1627466718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Party Colour</strong></h2>Beat all the boards, but measure your moves carefully or you’ll end up without any colours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/b5413f119a2038f3538d86f1d48cbc44.poster.avif?t=1627466718\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/b5413f119a2038f3538d86f1d48cbc44.webm?t=1627466718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669030/extras/b5413f119a2038f3538d86f1d48cbc44.mp4?t=1627466718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
